title: Skate Team
description: Check out Mark Appleyard, Danny Supa, Ryan Decenzo, Scott Decenzo and Willy Santos throwing down the fun in a ditch for this Arnette Skate Team edit. Not featured, but equally loved are Luis Tolentino and Team Captain, Pat Duffy.
